summary: Ok I don’t know why I never read Tapu Fini/Kapu-Rehire’s Pokedex but.... I’m actually very very intriqued of SM108 now. If you...
body:
Ok I don’t know why I never read Tapu Fini/Kapu-Rehire’s Pokedex but…. I’m actually very very intriqued of SM108 now. If you forgot, the name of the episode was revealed to be In Kapu-Rehire’s Mist.

Here are Tapu Fini’s Pokedex entries:

Look closely to the Sun Pokedex entry:

The dense fog it creates brings the downfall and destruction of its confused enemies.

…I have a feeling SM108 might indeed be a continuation to SM107, Kaki and Satoshi (maybe with Hapu) ending up in Kapu-Rehire’s mist, and needing to prove themselves to survive. Also the Ultra Moon entry:

Although it’s called a guardian deity, terrible calamities sometimes befall those who recklessly approach Tapu Fini.

I am officially scared of Kapu-Rehire/Tapu Fini now. Ohmygod Poni Arc is looking to be quite an arc. Do not mess with Tapu Fini!

summary: Y’know, we should be soon getting soundclip of the new ending song, Kokoro no note. I wonder if it’ll release tomorrow or on...
body:
Y’know, we should be soon getting soundclip of the new ending song, Kokoro no note. I wonder if it’ll release tomorrow or on saturday. When did Kimi no Boken get released again?

I tend to like giving songs an early listen so I can focus on the graphics instead during the episode airing :D And I’m very curious to hear this choir song, it’s sung by elementary schoolers, written by Taiiku Okazaki again, and like, overall the name of the song gives me a calm-like feeling. If you didn’t know, Kokoro no Note roughly translates to Notes of the Heart, or the Notebook of the Heart.

I’m just so excited for this weekend, Hapuuu, Plumeriii, new ending soong ;v;

summary:
Bulbasaur: Private Investigator - Chapter 8
“H...hi, Bulbasaur. How’ve you been?” 
“I’m... I’m really sorry about Reed.”
“It...
body:
Bulbasaur: Private Investigator - Chapter 8

“H…hi, Bulbasaur. How’ve you been?”

“I’m… I’m really sorry about Reed.”

“It wasn’t your fault.” It was. “And it was a long time ago.” It wasn’t.

“Psyduck said you were working on a case? You needed help?”

I didn’t want to work with her. I just wanted to get away.

“All my files are at my office.”

So I lied. Big deal.

“Oh! Let’s just go there, then!”

“No, I don’t…”

…

Teleport?

Show-off.

—————————————————————————————————

Check out previous chapters here!
